      <h1 class='title'>Departmental Staff</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1649WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1649ws' title='Col. 1649WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1649WS' name='column_1649ws' href='#column_1649ws' rel='bookmark'>1649WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_1'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-elfyn-llwyd' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_1' title='Link to this speech by Mr Elfyn Llwyd' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-elfyn-llwyd" title="Mr Elfyn Llwyd">Mr. Llwyd</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Wales how many staff are employed in the Wales Office; how many there were in 1997; and if he will make a statement. [188997]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_2'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-hain' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_2' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Hain' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-hain" title="Mr Peter Hain">Mr. Hain</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Staff numbers for the Wales Office, since its establishment on 1 July 1999, are shown in table 5.7 of the Wales Office Annual Report 2004 (Cm 6228), a copy of which can be obtained from the Library of the House.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
